title: Smart Scan - Main Menu

body.body: Click the MAIN MENU button to exit the Smart Scan area and return to the diagnostic tool Main Menu.
Upon returning to the Main Menu, all previously scanned motorcycle data will be cleared from memory. The tool will perform a full motorcycle scan upon returning to the Smart Scan area.
